headline: McDonald's (MCD): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: McDonald's trades at $296.15 and has moved in lockstep with the market. Its shares have returned 16.7% over the last six months while the S&P 500 has gained 13.1%.
